Title: JET Range 9510 DZR double regulating valve 32mm
Description: The JET Range 9510 double regulating valve with 32mm female threaded connections provides a correct balance between the different branches of a hydraulic heating or cooling system to be obtained. This valve can be used to regulate flow by modifying the position of the throttling disc via the rotating handwheel. The handwheel can be used to stop flow at any time and, when reopened, returns to the previous setting using a Memory Stop function.
